com.diogonunes.jcdp.color.api

Class Ansi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diogonunes.jcdp.color.api.Ansi

  • public class Ansi
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores enums used to generate a Ansi escape code. There is one enum for each component of the print format: Attribute, Foreground Color, Background Color.
    See Also:
    Ansi escape codes
